The paper deals with community-based question answering services, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed framework involves deep learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the potential applications of the framework, including expert finding, which falls under social and information networks (cs.SI).
